e>係咪輕度弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be712b0e01747d7b5e676378d45112cb19e1dc9c","tid":237851,"uid":29293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時諗野正正常常都會俾人話logical 但一講野就控制唔到咁"},{"pid":"98bd59d860ad9789ee6319e88f4f0786315150fd","tid":237851,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練習，寫多啲講稿<br />\n所謂既口才好多都係練定既對白嚟</blockquote><br />\n轉數快同口才好係咪成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉數快最常見既結果係講嘢唔經大腦得罪人"},{"pid":"49e40d7ac97f509f3ae2b63ec952a7b79514cf8d","tid":237851,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>練習，寫多啲講稿<br />\n所謂既口才好多都係練定既對白嚟</blockquote><br />\n轉數快同口才好係咪成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉數快最常見既結果係講嘢唔經大腦得罪人</blockquote><br />\n你轉數夠快就可以意識到講嘅野會得罪人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf2e1183e8996e0cb1f025fd303aad900938534","tid":237851,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:28:05.000Z","msg":"首先要讀多啲資訊性嘅書/文/鳩噏<br />\n唔同範疇都識啲<br />\n咁你個腦先有足夠嘅料去抽出嚟講<br />\n<br />\n之後就係練鳩噏<br />\n講乜都冇所謂<br />\n鳩都冇所謂<br />\n但一定要係清晰講出嚟<br />\n可以完全唔make sense<br />\n冇問題，呢part係要你練開口講野嘅自信<br />\n要令自己唔怕開口講野<del>唔怕講鳩野</del><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係掌握自己講野嘅節奏<br />\n寧願慢都唔好窒<br />\n細水長流好過<br />\n慢慢就可以加快<br />\nSlow to smooth, smooth to fast<br />\n<br />\n最重要係唔好怕樣衰<br />\n<br />\n你話講粗口嗰陣唔窒<br />\n一可能係你唔夠料要用粗口嚟填補<br />\n二可能係你唔夠膽講 爆粗變相壯膽<br />\n三可能係你講唔切 用粗口可以接駁好你啲字詞<br />\n<br />\n<del>其實出去街市買餸同啲阿嬸鳩噏就最練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del>"},{"pid":"24d699e7ff8f13e9e313e1861e41b6b609d1924d","tid":237851,"uid":81322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"有冇諗下學下思古井?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/239214/page/11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/239214/page/11</a>"},{"pid":"19d6b6b90bc7470c83616a08b593e34f40a33a0e","tid":237851,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先要讀多啲資訊性嘅書/文/鳩噏<br />\n唔同範疇都識啲<br />\n咁你個腦先有足夠嘅料去抽出嚟講<br />\n<br />\n之後就係練鳩噏<br />\n講乜都冇所謂<br />\n鳩都冇所謂<br />\n但一定要係清晰講出嚟<br />\n可以完全唔make sense<br />\n冇問題，呢part係要你練開口講野嘅自信<br />\n要令自己唔怕開口講野<del>唔怕講鳩野</del><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係掌握自己講野嘅節奏<br />\n寧願慢都唔好窒<br />\n細水長流好過<br />\n慢慢就可以加快<br />\nSlow to smooth, smooth to fast<br />\n<br />\n最重要係唔好怕樣衰<br />\n<br />\n你話講粗口嗰陣唔窒<br />\n一可能係你唔夠料要用粗口嚟填補<br />\n二可能係你唔夠膽講 爆粗變相壯膽<br />\n三可能係你講唔切 用粗口可以接駁好你啲字詞<br />\n<br />\n<del>其實出去街市買餸同啲阿嬸鳩噏就最練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del></blockquote><br />\n我覺得一二三都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5a0f0d4347608f9f8b84f386e7b8d25f006878","tid":237851,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:49:04.000Z","msg":"睇是冇用的<br />\n直接去搵份7仔 OK 一日同超過300個人講野，慢慢練"},{"pid":"560dc70d4205715b7ee45562f808e0e31275baff","tid":237851,"uid":45939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T23:17:13.000Z","msg":"樓主多唔多fd？"},{"pid":"85d9d38a9300751fce5db68919b0b2bf36e56db5","tid":237851,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:16:29.000Z","msg":"睇下鬼谷子 <br />\n教你辯論技巧<br />\n點樣說服人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fb47e5b54d1b3159c820ca4d611fc76612b528","tid":237851,"uid":51159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0